						<div class="postbody">After you've expanded your project's PRG ROM to four 8192-byte banks, here are two things to try:<br /><ul><li>The reset and NMI vectors need to go at the end of bank 3, not bank 1. </li><li>Have you tried putting at least some data in all four banks (0-3)? </li></ul></div>

