				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">PRG banks for NROM-128, which has 16384 bytes of PRG ROM, are located at $C000 and $E000. They are also mirrored into $8000 and $A000, but their canonical locations are $C000 and $E000.<br /><br />PRG banks for NROM-256, which has 32768 bytes of PRG ROM, are located at $8000, $A000, $C000, and $E000.<br /><br />Could you attach your code so that others can look at it to help you determine what's going wrong?</div>

