						<div class="postbody">Your vectors are in the wrong bank. You're trying to put stuff that goes at $FFFA in the bank that contains $A000-$BFFF.<br /><br />Because of the vectors (and hardwired banks in case there's bankswitching), when expanding ROMs we often add new banks to the beginning, not the end.</div>

